    We live in a post-boredom world. There are no limit of the things that want our attention. Even worse, a lot of people make a lot of money off of this human weakness. Identify and eliminate distractions from your life to be more productive.
  &#34;I would’ve said I never read blogs or anything like that on the internet, and that saves a huge amount of time ... Try to protect your time. When it&#39;s time for work, I do the work rather than goof off on the internet&#34;
